{"id":8222,"date":"2026-02-03T10:12:59","date_gmt":"2026-02-03T03:12:59","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=8222"},"modified":"2026-02-03T10:12:59","modified_gmt":"2026-02-03T03:12:59","slug":"ceramide-phuc-hoi-hang-rao-va-giu-am","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/ceramide-phuc-hoi-hang-rao-va-giu-am\/","title":{"rendered":"Ceramide \u2013 Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o v\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean cho l\u00e0n da"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu v\u00ed l\u00e0n da nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng, th\u00ec ceramide ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u201cxi m\u0103ng sinh h\u1ecdc\u201d gi\u00fap g\u1eafn k\u1ebft c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng v\u1edbi nhau, ng\u0103n n\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ed1c h\u01a1i v\u00e0 ch\u1eb7n vi khu\u1ea9n \u2013 ch\u1ea5t k\u00edch \u1ee9ng x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp. S\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t ceramide l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn da kh\u00f4, bong tr\u00f3c, \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t ho\u1eb7c nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m m\u00e3n t\u00ednh.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-quan-ve-ceramide\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 Ceramide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc: Ceramides l\u00e0 nh\u00f3m sphingolipid t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 trong l\u1edbp s\u1eebng c\u1ee7a da (stratum corneum), chi\u1ebfm kho\u1ea3ng 50% tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng lipid \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c &amp; l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng: Ceramide \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 1980 trong nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Khi khoa h\u1ecdc t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ceramide \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh (nh\u01b0 Ceramide NP, AP, EOP, NS, NG, AS, NH, EOS), ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vai tr\u00f2 sinh h\u1ecdc: Gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc, duy tr\u00ec t\u00ednh to\u00e0n v\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a l\u1edbp s\u1eebng, v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o khi da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ceramide kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5t \u201cd\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t\u201d th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 l\u00e0 lipid c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac n\u1ed9i sinh \u2013 thi\u1ebfu n\u00f3, m\u1ecdi d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-hoat-chat-ceramide\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t Ceramide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da: gi\u00fap t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o lipid gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng, l\u00e0m da kh\u1ecfe, gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1eef \u1ea9m s\u00e2u: h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf TEWL (Transepidermal Water Loss) &#8211; m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc qua bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng &amp; \u0111\u1ecf: da \u0111\u1ee7 ceramide s\u1ebd \u00edt ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi acid, retinoid ho\u1eb7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb: th\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 cho vi\u00eam da c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ecba, rosacea, da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, sau peel\/laser.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8224\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8224\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8224 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-2.webp\" alt=\"Ceramide \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 nh\u01b0 xi m\u0103ng li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8224\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ceramide \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 nh\u01b0 xi m\u0103ng li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ceramide k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi cholesterol v\u00e0 acid b\u00e9o t\u1ef1 do (FFA) t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh m\u00e0ng lipid. C\u1ea5u tr\u00fac n\u00e0y bao b\u1ecdc t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng, gi\u00fap:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t b\u00ean trong<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u0103n vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t k\u00edch \u1ee9ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o l\u1edbp s\u1eebng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu thi\u1ebfu ceramide (do tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, t\u1ea9y r\u1eeda m\u1ea1nh, b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd da\u2026), h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da n\u1ee9t v\u1ee1 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, bong tr\u00f3c, \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t, d\u1ec5 vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-loai-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf &amp; lo\u1ea1i\u00a0 th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ceramide t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean: chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb ngu\u1ed3n th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt ho\u1eb7c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p sinh h\u1ecdc, c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng da ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ceramide t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh danh c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 (NP, EOP, AP\u2026).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p chu\u1ea9n: Ceramide + Cholesterol + Acid b\u00e9o theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng ~3:1:1 (theo nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u1ee7a Dr. Peter Elias \u2013 UCSF).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea1ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m: kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, serum, lotion, cleanser ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00f4i khi c\u00f3 trong s\u1eefa t\u1eafm cho da kh\u00f4\/vi\u00eam da c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ecba.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"su-dung-ceramide-sao-cho-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Ceramide sao cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-tuong-su-dung\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4, bong, s\u1ea7n, \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t, ho\u1eb7c da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m m\u00e3n t\u00ednh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da sau peel, laser, \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n ho\u1eb7c d\u00f9ng retinoid.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o (s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng acid\/retinol th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u1ebb nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 vi\u00eam da c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ecba c\u0169ng d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c (theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u00e1c s\u0129).<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8225\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8225\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8225 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-3.webp\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Ceramide\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8225\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Ceramide<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/kem-phuc-hoi-thai-doc-da-gsc\/\">Kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da y\u1ebfu GSC<\/a><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-dung-%e2%80%93-lieu-luong\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng \u2013 li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m: d\u00f9ng sau serum ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t (ho\u1eb7c ngay sau r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t n\u1ebfu routine t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t: 1\u20132 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y (s\u00e1ng &amp; t\u1ed1i).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1: l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch &#8211; toner nh\u1eb9 (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3) &#8211; serum &#8211; kem ch\u1ee9a ceramide &#8211; ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng (ban ng\u00e0y).\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: lu\u00f4n thoa tr\u00ean da h\u01a1i \u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u201ckh\u00f3a \u1ea9m\u201d.<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng: c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c m\u1ec1m \u2013 \u1ea9m c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n sau 3\u20135 ng\u00e0y, h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i r\u00f5 sau 2\u20134 tu\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-hop-ceramide-sao-cho-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p Ceramide sao cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>Ceramide + Panthenol\/B5:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, gi\u1ea3m kh\u00f4.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ceramide + Niacinamide:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p ceramide n\u1ed9i sinh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ceramide + HA:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m t\u1ea7ng n\u00f4ng + kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m t\u1ea7ng s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ceramide + Retinol ho\u1eb7c AHA\/BHA:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gi\u00fap da dung n\u1ea1p actives t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ceramide + Madecassoside\/Centella:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u0103ng t\u00ednh l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, th\u00edch h\u1ee3p da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-chong-chi-dinh\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd &amp; Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n cao: kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng, kh\u00f4ng m\u00f9i, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n dung m\u00f4i c\u1ed3n \u2013 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ecf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sai s\u00f3t th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p: d\u00f9ng ch\u1ed3ng l\u1edbp qu\u00e1 d\u00e0y (nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 da d\u1ea7u) g\u00e2y b\u00ed da, n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n; n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea1ng lotion nh\u1eb9 ho\u1eb7c kem nh\u0169 m\u1ecfng n\u1ebfu l\u00e0 da d\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng sai n\u1ec1n: ceramide ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t khi c\u00f3 cholesterol + fatty b\u00e9o, c\u00f2n \u201c\u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9c\u201d hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 k\u00e9m h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8226\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8226\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8226 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-4.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ceramide kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ceramide-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8226\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ceramide kh\u00f4ng?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3. Ceramide l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem an to\u00e0n tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i khi d\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i da, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 trong thai k\u1ef3 ho\u1eb7c cho con b\u00fa. C\u00e1c d\u00f2ng \u201cdermo-cosmetic\u201d ho\u1eb7c baby lotion ch\u1ee9a ceramide v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb cho nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o:<\/p>\n<p><i>What are Ceramides in Skincare &amp; its Benefits? | CeraVe\u00ae Australia<\/i>. (n.d.). Www.cerave.com.au. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cerave.com.au\/skin-care-ingredients\/ceramides\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/www.cerave.com.au\/skin-care-ingredients\/ceramides<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u200c<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ceramide \u2013 ph\u00e2n t\u1eed lipid t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da, gi\u1eef vai tr\u00f2 then ch\u1ed1t trong vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, gi\u1eef \u1ea9m v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":8223,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8222","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8222","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8222"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8222\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":8241,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8222\/revisions\/8241"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/8223"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\